News.Title: Freshara Agro Exports: Shares List at 16% Premium on NSE SME
News.Summary: Freshara Agro Exports shares debuted on NSE SME at ₹135, a 16.3% premium to the IPO price of ₹116. The ₹75.39 crore IPO was oversubscribed 236.80 times. The company plans to use the funds for capital expenditure, working capital, and general corporate purposes.
